short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Save Lineups from Daily Fantasy Sports Rankings and insert them into FanDuel.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: The DFSR Lineup Exporter allows you to create, save, and paste the line-ups you've created with their lineup construction tool directly into FanDuel with the click of a button. No more clicking back and forth between tabs!
